ed="T" n="0848b23"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0848b23"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>明州奉化縣<persName key="A012858">契此</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0848b24"/><persName key="A012858">釋契此</persName>者，不詳氏族，或云<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>人也。形裁<lb
ed="T" n="0848b25"/>腲脮，蹙頞皤腹，言語無恒，寢臥隨處。常以<lb
ed="T" n="0848b26"/>杖荷布囊入鄽肆，見物則乞，至于醯醬<ptr type="glossary" target="#g225"/>魚<lb
ed="T" n="0848b27"/>𦵔，纔接入口，分少許入囊，號為<persName key="A012858">長汀子<lb
ed="T" n="0848b28"/>布袋師</persName>也。曾於雪中臥，而身上無雪，人以<lb
ed="T" n="0848b29"/>此奇之。有偈云：「<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>真<persName key="A001428">彌勒</persName>。<ptr target="#n638"/>」時人皆不識<pb ed="T" n="0848c" xml:id="T50.2061.0848c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0848c01"/>等句。人言<persName key="A001428">慈<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>垂迹也。又於大橋上<ptr target="#n639"/>立，或<lb
ed="T" n="0848c02"/>問：「<ref type="person" target="#A012858">和尚</ref>在此何為？」曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A012858">我</ref>在此覓人。」常就人<lb
ed="T" n="0848c03"/>乞啜<ptr target="#n640"/>，其店則物售。袋囊中皆百一供身具也。<lb
ed="T" n="0848c04"/>示人吉凶，必現相表兆。亢陽，即曳高齒木<lb
ed="T" n="0848c05"/>屐，市橋上竪膝而眠。水潦，則係<anchor xml:id="beg0848002"/>濕<anchor xml:id="end0848002"/>草屨。人<lb
ed="T" n="0848c06"/>以此驗知。以<date notBefore-iso="+0901-05-18" key="j20502812051391" notAfter-iso="+0904-06-01"><name>天復</name>中</date>終于<placeName key="PL000000012481">奉川</placeName><ptr target="#n641"/>，鄉邑共埋<lb
ed="T" n="0848c07"/>之。後有他州見<ref type="person" target="#A012858">此公</ref>，亦荷布袋行。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000009926 #PL000000018627">江</ref>、<ref type="place" target="#PL000000011308 #PL000000008363">浙</ref>之<lb
ed="T" n="0848c08"/>間多圖畫其像焉。</p>
